{"tid":1329831,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"佢好愛我 但係我唔想離開","createTime":"2019-07-18T10:25:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T10:26:47.000Z","uid":250432,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2526cd0e1d02ba878d1f3512e78cbc04e18104e7","tid":1329831,"uid":250432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T10:25:26.000Z","msg":"有少少嘢想請教大家<br />\n<br />\n我同男朋友一起三個月 雖然中間有爭吵 不過佢好愛我 好快已經求婚  但係佢好唔鍾意香港 覺得呢度冇未來 佢好想移民去一些生活成本低嘅國家生活 自從送中嘅事情之後 去日日都提起移民 最近仲想辭埋份工.......<br />\n<br />\n但我唔想離開香港 而且三個月係咪足夠令我睇清佢係咩人 如果我跟佢走 我一定會同成家翻曬面 到時佢離開我等等 我連最後嘅家都冇........"},{"pid":"bbc163b28a172150844b449b111265a67ba1c0a1","tid":1329831,"uid":198990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T10:26:47.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">【香城OL wiki】史上最全攻略！！持續更新！！</span></strong> <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=16jsUWJDS0YTIlICECOfDtzKt4XIgJVuzER0c0I4wFQ4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D16jsUWJDS0YTIlICECOfDtzKt4XIgJVuzER0c0I4wFQ4&d=MciEVzKn1v3nDYmPhzNAyk6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=40888838\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=16jsUWJDS0YTIlICECOfDtzKt4XIgJVuzER0c0I4wFQ4</a>"}]}